{"tid":1927121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍持有的「AA39」車輛被發現將狗放在車斗中行駛","createTime":"2020-03-15T14:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:16:02.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"861121d7edb9210f04e75805d5b598989cb32d1a","tid":1927121,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/15/224242_f85e1514aa0cd01ff5bd2c40fe9e23a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2F224242_f85e1514aa0cd01ff5bd2c40fe9e23a8.png&h=5adb5521&s={SIZE}\" />懷疑成龍持有的「AA39」車輛，再次被人發現將狗狗放在車斗上！目擊者表示，於今晚6時56分於觀塘往將軍澳方向的隧道，見到一輛車牌AA39的爬山車後座開逢車斗放了一隻秋田犬，估計車速達6、70公里，狗狗狀甚驚慌，險象還生，目擊者坦言希望有關部門可以跟進。「AA39」車輛以前曾多次被發現將狗狗放於車斗中行駛，包括2016年4月便被人目擊將兩隻金毛尋回犬放在車斗中，行駛時並無任何安全狗狗的措施。愛護動物協會曾指有關做法會令狗狗和道路使用者都處於危險情況。<br />\n<br />\n本報在2016年4月曾報道過同一輛車將兩隻金毛尋回犬放在車斗中。當時該車輛登記車主為一間名為「Shire Horse Co. Ltd」的私人公司，公司董事為原名陳港生的成龍、其妻子林鳳嬌及兒子房祖名。<br />\n<br />\n愛協曾指有關做法置狗狗於危險環境，如狗狗受驚跳出車外，更可能引起道路安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n香港《道路交通條例》並沒有規管車斗載動物的問題，惟《道路交通（交通管制）規例》列明，車輛的任何負載物必須適當地固定在車輛上，若將該狗視為物品，沒有為狗綁好繩帶已構成犯法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%96%91%E6%88%90%E9%BE%8D%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%9B%E5%86%8D%E5%B0%87%E7%8B%97%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8A%E6%96%97%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%8C%E9%A7%9B-%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%B0%E7%8A%AC%E7%8B%80%E7%94%9A%E9%A9%9A%E6%85%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BC%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2596%2597%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A7%258B%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%258A%25AC%25E7%258B%2580%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%2585%258C%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=b6ad7938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BC%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2596%2597%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A7%258B%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%258A%25AC%25E7%258B%2580%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%2585%258C%2F&h=0430d215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%96%91%E6%88%90%E9%BE%8D%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%9B%E5%86%8D%E5%B0%87%E7%8B%97%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8A%E6%96%97%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%8C%E9%A7%9B-%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%B0%E7%8A%AC%E7%8B%80%E7%94%9A%E9%A9%9A%E6%85%8C/</a>"},{"pid":"1cc28956838221d9a54abd0ca6f697627d8cfe0a","tid":1927121,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"有咩事鄧炳強會赴湯蹈火去幫成龍"},{"pid":"e9329408c0c616e6b0447c72e43043f574f402dc","tid":1927121,"uid":169994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"遇到白炸打個電話無事啦"},{"pid":"004c6e16dec55a414b8776619e79ddc89d61a5ca","tid":1927121,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"成龍抱住2警合照"},{"pid":"a541fbe96ac82a0435289594cc8771985c09948f","tid":1927121,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc28956838221d9a54abd0ca6f697627d8cfe0a","tid":1927121,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"有咩事鄧炳強會赴湯蹈火去幫成龍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/112188_o20copy_ZbjS1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t